\fs42 \cf0 Basics:\
	Drawing World is a program designed to work with voice control. You mouse is you main tool, while to switch what that tool does you use your voice. There are 3 main modes, each with different commands: Draw,Select, Camera. These instructions are separated by each section and their respective commands. Changing setting can be seen in the tool indicator, interface, or cursor to facilitate know what you have done. Additionally, this program can be used without voice control (toggled by pressing \'91v\'92 or saying \'91disable voice controls\'92), albeit certain limitations as it is only for demonstration purposes; the keybindings for which can be found in the project folder. \

