\fs42 In drawing mode:\
    The main mode, lets you draw, create shapes, and import props,
\fs20 \
 	
\fs42 - Say the name of a color to make it your current color (ROYGBV and black,white,gray)\
	- Say \cf2 increase\cf0 /\cf3 decrease\cf0  followed by the what you want to \cf2 increase\cf0 /\cf3 decrease\cf0  the size of (line,shape,prop)\
	- Say \cf4 create\cf0  followed by the shape you want to create (triangle,square,circle)\
	- Say \cf5 import\cf0  prop followed by the prop you want to use\
	- Say \cf6 grab\cf0  to be able to grab and individual object (Say draw to disable when done)\
	- Say \cf7 select\cf0  to enter select mode \
	- Say \cf8 clear\cf0  to clear you canvas\
	- Say \cf9 camera\cf0  to enter camera mode\
	- Say \cf10 remove background\cf0  to remove the background\
	- Say \cf11 save\cf0  to save whatever is on your canvas as an image to the project folder\
